{"tid":1002654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陰謀敗露】佛州路陷 驚揭有人挖隧道圖劫銀行","createTime":"2019-01-31T06:04:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T14:57:07.000Z","uid":130626,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"755b6916927debf1a29bc33e6640c34b99b1aae9","tid":1002654,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:04:31.000Z","msg":"美國佛羅里達州周二路陷，當工人接報到場後驚揭下方有一條隧道，於是通知警方，揭發原來有不法之徒企圖挖隧道打劫銀行。<br />\n這條隧道出現在彭布羅克派恩（Pembroke Pines），工人周二晚9時半接報稱路上出現路陷，趕到現場後發現路陷洞口內有一條電線，通往一個樹木繁茂的地區，於是報警。<br />\n聯邦調查局（FBI）周三表示，這條長46米的隧道是通往一間位於商場內的銀行，認為犯案的不只一人，而疑犯僅用鋤頭挖掘，但警方強調目前隧道洞口太小，洞口直徑大約僅60至90厘米，相信未有人曾成功穿過，包括挖洞者。<br />\nFBI相信當地周末下雨導致路面下陷，洞口入口以木板覆蓋，現場亦發現小拖車及一部小型發電機，另外當局曾派出搜索犬搜查，隧道內未有發現屍體。<br />\n調查員坦言目前對案件毫無頭緒，不清楚歹徒對上一次行動是何時，也未找到疑犯，當局會繼續調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548899671_ec9d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548899671_ec9d.jpg&h=ce56396c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548899439_8c25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548899439_8c25.jpg&h=8d8c292d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548899671_7da0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548899671_7da0.jpg&h=14be58a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548899671_a2e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548899671_a2e6.jpg&h=ab3ce141&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190131/large/1548899439_f62a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190131%2Flarge%2F1548899439_f62a.jpg&h=29156f3f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"dd3bfba23e9885fe63bb307ce8bf057bb06db8a2","tid":1002654,"uid":78016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:05:50.000Z","msg":"ocean eleven <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪偷左啦已經"},{"pid":"704ae018604d9d3fb55066f8e50b8628e948b5b4","tid":1002654,"uid":4575,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"當佢地知道香港原來打個電話就呃到幾億，會唔會覺得自己掘隧道打劫銀行好戇鳩"},{"pid":"cb369b526b8e71f39ee99873e5811a2a57f2d129","tid":1002654,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"paper house"},{"pid":"a8419aeadb38d11ec381769f3da170c8ffc604b5","tid":1002654,"uid":108347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704ae018604d9d3fb55066f8e50b8628e948b5b4","tid":1002654,"uid":4575,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"當佢地知道香港原來打個電話就呃到幾億，會唔會覺得自己掘隧道打劫銀行好戇鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:10:06.000Z","msg":"真係dna唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e899fbeb54a4c490fb7a49760cfe608fae1835a4","tid":1002654,"uid":187544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"704ae018604d9d3fb55066f8e50b8628e948b5b4","tid":1002654,"uid":4575,"like":43,"dislike":0,"score":43,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:07:26.000Z","msg":"當佢地知道香港原來打個電話就呃到幾億，會唔會覺得自己掘隧道打劫銀行好戇鳩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T06:10:36.000Z","msg":"扮下大陸公安，幾十億都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f5e3d47459ac8965b1e51ad7edfe802951d8f2e","tid":1002654,"uid":141869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-31T07:00:16.000Z","msg":"咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi